column5: I have tried BPS, Gander Mountain, Cabelas. Dick's anymore ideas?  Looking for good slection and good prices.

If you want mail order try one of the musky shops.. pastika, rollie & helens  if in toronto, JBs fishing depot on ronson dr or tightline out in pickering.  LeBaron has best prices but limited selection.
Fishbait! Sent you a PM! Paul.
LOL Robin you took the words right out of my mind!  Whopper
Best price is probably www.protacklemuskyshop.com  Stacy ships in three days, if he doesn't have what you order he will call you and let you know what is available...
spring fishing show is coming up, its where most of my baits get purchased for the year
jeez, if everybody keeps goin in my tackle box, I'LL soon be lookin for a spot to buy Suicks
